SectionBody.Text: In addition to the supplemental corporate fee of $88.75 imposed pursuant to s. 607.193, the fees of the Department of State under this act are as follows:

Subsection.Text: For furnishing a certified copy, $52.50 for the first 15 pages plus $1.00 for each additional page.
For filing an original certificate of limited partnership, $965.
For filing an original application for registration as a foreign limited partnership, $965.
For filing certificate of merger, $52.50 for each party thereto.

For filing a reinstatement, $500 for each calendar year or part thereof the limited partnership was administratively dissolved or foreign limited partnership was revoked in the records of the Department of State.

Paragraph.Text: Changing a registered agent or registered office address, $35;
Resigning as a registered agent, $87.50; or
Of amendment or restatement of the certificate of limited partnership, $52.50;

Subsection.Text: For filing a statement of termination, $52.50.
For filing a notice of cancellation for foreign limited partnership, $52.50.
For furnishing a certificate of status or authorization, $8.75.
For filing a certificate of dissolution, $52.50.
For filing a certificate of revocation of dissolution, $52.50.
For filing any other domestic or foreign limited partnership document, $52.50.
